                <div class="faq-item">
                    <h3 class="title">What do I need to open an account at Shopintoit?</h3>
                    <p class="content">Any one with items to sell can create an account at Shopintoit. All you need are some photos of the items that you wish to sell. Or have those images ready on your Pinterest account. Also, you will need a payment method. We support Paypal for now.</p>
