                    <h3 class="title">What information do I need to provide on my items?</h3>
                    <p class="content">We will ask you the following information for your items:<br/>
                        <b>Title</b>– You can re-use the title of your Pinned image or re-write it. This title is displayed below the image and used in the shopping cart and receipt.<br/>
                        <b>Sale Price</b> – Your item sales price before taxes.<br/>
                        <b>Standard Shipping Price</b>– this is the most common cost that you item have. You have the option to offer international & domestic. We also have express and priority shipping available.<br/>
